snippet.title: Mike Patey
snippet.description: Join Mike Patey as he builds some of the most incredible experimental aircraft on the planet! Mike is a father, husband, engineer, fabricator, and aviator. Mike's latest aircraft is a modified Carbon Cub named Scrappy.
